text.tspan: Israel: Weekly confirmed COVID-19 cases by age, Dec 18, 2020 to Mar 16,
New confirmed cases are shown as the rolling weekly sum. Data is available at the national level, plus breakdown by regions
where vaccination began early or late.
Vaccination in Israel began on December 19 2020. Israel imposed a third national lockdown on January 8 2021.
